_sText:
This is the second map i have created, releasing this one as so far its 50 votes YES and 4 votes NO in the server map question vote ;)

It is a complete remake of a shotty map for gungame, a very slight amount bigger, plenty of snow, snowmen and a few special features for some added 'nade and knife fighting suprises!

A bit more than the standard shotty map, and isn't too large to upset you users either!
